item.description:
No Static plays Steely Dan once again! This time at Ryles in Inman Square in Cambridge. Listening and dancing to a fantastic band that truly sounds just like Steely Dan is becoming a regular event for Sitz.

From the web site - "For this special show NO STATIC will be presenting a cavalcade of the greatest DAN Hits from four decades of incredible songwriting." It begins at 9:00PM. There is a $12 cover.

Hope to see you for one of their first shows of the year!

Please note, parking can be a bit of a challenge in the area but is available on side streets, and the fun you'll have will be worth it. (smile)

Happy New Year!
item.name: Another Night with No Static - Cancelled
